name: Bennie Thompson
summary: A staffer for Congressman Bennie Thompson was fired after posting controversial remarks on Facebook in response to the recent shooting incident involving former President Trump. The staffer stated, "Don't miss next time." The post drew widespread criticism, leading to Representative Thompson's decision to terminate the staffer's employment. This incident has sparked backlash against Thompson, with calls for his resignation due to his previous attempt to reduce Trump's security detail. Amidst this controversy, Thompson has reaffirmed his support for Biden's nomination and urged unity within the party. Additionally, investigations are ongoing by the Secret Service regarding the staffer's actions, and both the state auditor and members of the GOP are demanding Thompson's resignation for his role in the Secret Service billing issue and his staffer's posts.

summary: The 2024 MLB Home Run Derby will showcase some of baseball's top sluggers, including two-time champion Pete Alonso. The field features several notable participants, including the Rangers' Adolis Garcia and Teoscar Hernández. The Derby will take place at Nationals Park on Monday, July 17th, as part of the All-Star week festivities. Fans can watch the event live on ESPN and listen on ESPN Radio. The format of the Derby includes three rounds, with each round featuring a head-to-head matchup between two batters. The batter with the most home runs in each matchup advances to the next round. The final round will determine the champion. Betting odds and rules for the event are available online.

name: Pocono Raceway
summary: The 2024 Pocono Raceway pit stall assignments have been announced, setting the stage for the NASCAR weekend at Pocono. NBC Philadelphia provides a comprehensive schedule, watch guide, and analysis of favorites and picks for the race, while USA TODAY reports on Ryan Blaney's victory over Denny Hamlin. The Pocono Record covers traffic updates on Route 115 due to the Great American Getaway 400 on Sunday. Tennessean offers live updates, highlights, and a live leaderboard of the NASCAR Cup Series race at Pocono. WNEP highlights the campers who have set up at Pocono Raceway. NBC Sports provides insights into what to watch for in the NASCAR Cup race, and the Daytona Beach News-Journal lists the NASCAR schedule and broadcasts for the Cup, Xfinity, and Truck Series at Pocono. Hendrick Motorsports previews the paint schemes for the race, and NASCAR confirms Ryan Blaney's second Cup Series win of 2024, defeating Hamlin and Bowman at Pocono.

name: Travis Bazzana
summary: In a historic move, the Cleveland Guardians selected Travis Bazzana, an Australian second baseman with a background in cricket, as the top overall pick in the 2024 MLB Draft. Bazzana's selection marks a significant milestone for both the Guardians organization and Australian baseball. The 18-year-old infielder, who honed his skills at Oregon State University, has been widely praised for his exceptional athleticism, fielding prowess, and offensive potential. This groundbreaking move signals the growing recognition of international talent and the increasing global reach of the MLB.
